.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-2::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: turquise, coral, yellow, light-blue, lavender, aquamarine
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig, mouse, pony, turtle
 1. the person who likes light-blue is not the owner of the turtle##6
 2. the owner of the turtle is in an even position##4
 3. the owner of the pony is not to the right of the owner of the mouse##8
 4. the person who likes yellow is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the owner of the turtle is between the person who likes light-blue and the owner of the goat##2
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 7. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the right of the person who likes yellow##5
 8. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
 9. the person who likes coral is not the owner of the mouse##6
10. the person who likes turquise is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person who likes lavender is not to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
12. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the person who likes lavender##8
13. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise##3
14. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
15. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the person who likes light-blue##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |      3       |   4    |    5    |    6    |
| Color   | yellow | aquamarine | coral | lavender | light-blue | turquise |
| Pet     | guinea-pig  | chinchilla  | goat         | turtle | pony    | mouse   |

