.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-3::.
There are 6 different nationalities: american, argentine, british, canadian, polish, spanish
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, alhambra, blend, pall-mall, vegafina, old-henry
 1. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the left of the british##5
 2. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the alhambra-smoker##5
 3. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
 4. the blend-smoker is not to the left of the argentine##8
 5. the british is somewhere to the left of the old-henry-smoker##5
 6. the spanish is on the left or right of the british##3
 7. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere to the right of the british##5
 8. the canadian is not to the right of the canadian##8
 9. the american is somewhere to the right of the british##5
10. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far right##1
11. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere between the polish and the blend-smoker##7
12. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the left of the blend-smoker##5
13. the spanish is between the vegafina-smoker and the old-henry-smoker##2
14. the argentine is on the right of the canadian##1
15. the blend-smoker is somewhere between the old-henry-smoker and the american##7
16. the vegafina-smoker is not to the left of the vegafina-smoker##8
17. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the right of the vegafina-smoker##5
18. the polish is the alhambra-smoker##1
19. the blend-smoker is not the american##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |       4       |     5     |    6     |
| Nationality   | polish   | british | spanish    | canadian      | argentine | american |
| Cigar         | alhambra | vegafina  | baccarat | old-henry | blend   | pall-mall  |

