 2. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
 3. the person eating zucchini is between the person driving the train and the person eating eggplant##2
 4. the person eating radish is in an even position##4
 5. the person eating zucchini is somewhere between the person eating tomato and the person driving the tram##7
 6. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
 7. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
 8. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the person eating zucchini##8
 9. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
10. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
11. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
12. the person driving the train is somewhere between the person driving the roller and the person eating zucchini##7
13. the person driving the roller is not to the right of the person driving the skateboard##8
14. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
15. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4
16. the person eating pomegranate is in an even position##4
17. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person eating zucchini##5

.:: Answer ::.
